===Etymology===
{{inh+|ro|la|mergo|mergere}}, itself ultimately from {{der|ro|ine-pro|*mesg-||to plunge, dip}}, with a unique sense developing in Balkanic or Eastern Romance. Compare {{cog|rup|njergu}}; cf. also {{cog|sq|mërgoj||to move away}} and {{cog|sc|imbergere||to push}}. The semantic shift could be owed to confusion with {{m|la|pergō|pergere}} or {{m|la|meō|meāre}}.

